<title>USA: National City Banc to buy back shares.</title>
<headline>National City Banc to buy back shares.</headline>
<dateline>EVANSVILLE, Ind. 1996-12-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>National City Bancshares Inc said Monday its directors authorized the repurchase during the 1997 year at market prices of up to five percent of the company's nine million common shares outstanding.</p>
<p>The shares are intended for use in a future stock dividend, the company said in a statement.</p>
<p>National City last paid a stock dividend of five percent on December 9.</p>
<p>Shares of National City were trading off 1/4 to 29-1/2.</p>
<p>		((Chicago newsdesk 312 408 8787))</p>
